headline.print_headline: Obama Says Michelle Obama Will Not Run for President
headline.main: Obama Says Michelle Obama Will Not Run for President

docs.lead_paragraph: It used to be that death and taxes were the only certain things in life, but for President Barack Obama there is a third: Michelle Obama will not run for president.
docs.snippet: It used to be that death and taxes were the only certain things in life, but for President Barack Obama there is a third: Michelle Obama will not run for president.

headline.print_headline: Head of U.S. Sugar Group Resigns Amid Crackdown on Sweetener
headline.main: Head of U.S. Sugar Group Resigns Amid Crackdown on Sweetener

docs.lead_paragraph: The head of the main U.S. sugar marketing lobby has stepped down after nearly 13 years, leaving the powerful industry group at a time of growing public concern about the health effects of excessive consumption of sweeteners.
